---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Consultation">
  <h1>Consultation</h1>
  <p>
    I offer expert consultation services to help you navigate the complexities of 
    software development and make informed technical decisions. Whether you're starting 
    a new project or optimizing an existing one, I provide strategic guidance tailored 
    to your specific challenges and goals.
  </p>
  <p>My consultation areas include:</p>
  <div class="grid" style="gap: 2rem;">
    <service-card title="Technology Strategy">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Strategic guidance on technology choices, architecture decisions, and 
          long-term technical roadmaps. I help you select the right tools and 
          frameworks for sustainable growth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
    <service-card title="Code Review & Audits">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Comprehensive code reviews and technical audits to identify improvements, 
          security vulnerabilities, and performance bottlenecks in your existing codebase.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
    <service-card title="Project Planning">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Expert project planning and timeline estimation. I help break down complex 
          requirements into manageable phases with realistic deliverables and milestones.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
    <service-card title="Performance Optimization">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Deep-dive analysis of application performance with actionable recommendations 
          for optimization. From database queries to frontend rendering efficiency.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
    <service-card title="Team Mentoring">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Technical mentoring for development teams, including best practices, 
          code standards, and knowledge transfer sessions to elevate team capabilities.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
    <service-card title="Problem Solving">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Targeted problem-solving sessions for specific technical challenges. 
          I provide practical solutions and implementation strategies for complex issues.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
  </div>
</Layout>
<script>
  import "@components/card/service-card";
</script>
